title: SMNTY Classics: Bisexuality: Part 2
itunes:title: SMNTY Classics: Bisexuality: Part 2
description:
In the second part of our classic bisexuality episode, our expert guests return with advice and resources for bisexual folks, and share some personal experience and even a bi-ku (bisexual haiku) along the way.
